<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/526250-is-the-black-cauldron-the-book-of-the">Is the &quot;Black Cauldron&quot; the book of the animated movie from the 80&#39;s?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_526250'><a id="like_count_community_question_526250" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/526250?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">4 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F24780.The_Book_of_Three">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/526250-is-the-black-cauldron-the-book-of-the">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/526250-is-the-black-cauldron-the-book-of-the">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
